{"type":"message","id":"240c56c0","parentId":"6049cfc4","timestamp":"2026-03-20T11:42:05.990Z","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"type":"text","text":"[Fri 2026-03-20 19:42 GMT+8] [Subagent Context] You are running as a subagent (depth 1/1). Results auto-announce to your requester; do not busy-poll for status.\n\n[Subagent Task]: 尚书省，介绍一下你的职能和工作方式。你能处理哪些类型的任务？请用简洁的语言说明。"}],"timestamp":1774006925986}}
{"type":"message","id":"9eecf85f","parentId":"240c56c0","timestamp":"2026-03-20T11:42:19.812Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"The user (taizi/main agent) is asking me to introduce myself as 尚书省 (the Shangshu Province/Department) - my role and capabilities, and what types of tasks I can handle. I should respond in character based on the SOUL.md and AGENTS.md context, keeping it concise.","thinkingSignature":"94473d43b3ab546668c13001ccc59a8ca0be873ca8f5126d4c633e047613712c"},{"type":"text","text":"<final>\n\n尚书省已接旨。\n\n## 职能定位\n\n我是**尚书省**，事务分发与协作中枢。负责接收圣旨（任务指令），判断类型，分发给合适的部门或仆从执行，并追踪结果回奏圣上。\n\n## 工作方式\n\n```\n圣旨传入 → 判断类型 → 分发执行 → 追踪结果 → 回奏圣上\n```\n\n## 可处理的任务类型\n\n| 类型 | 说明 |\n|------|------|\n| **简单问答** | 直接回复，无需创建任务 |\n| **信息查询** | 搜索文档、消息、用户等 |\n| **事务创建** | 在看板上创建 JJC 任务，分发给执行仆从 |\n| **飞书操作** | 日历、文档、多维表格、消息等 |\n| **复杂任务** | 拆解为目标，转派中书省或其他仆从 |\n\n## 核心原则\n\n- 🔍 **先判断**：消息 vs 事务，简单 vs 复杂\n- ✅ **自己能做的**：直接处理，不建任务\n- 🤝 **需要协作的**：创建 JJC 任务后转给执行部门\n- 📢 **回奏机制**：事务完成后必须在原对话中回复圣上\n\n一句话概括：**承上启下，分发事务，追踪结果**。\n\n</final>"}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":120,"output":333,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":34050,"totalTokens":34503,"cost":{"input":0.000048,"output":0.0004995,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0.0051075,"total":0.005655}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1774006925989}}
